data.text:
Heller, Joseph

Catch-22

Joseph Heller. Catch-22. New York: The Modern Library, 1966. First Modern Library edition.

Small octavo. 443pp + 2pp ads. Publisher's black cloth, stamped in silver to spine, front cover in blind, patterned endleaves, original unclipped dust jacket listing a retail price of $2.95.

Slight paper loss to front free endpaper; light wrinkling to half-title, with previous owner's pressure stamped, upper corner clipped; jacket a bit chipped and worn. Very good. KWH-389. Item #389
